description: Don't miss out on Special 5% Financing Offered at The Residences at 527 E 7th Street! Located in South Boston’s premier new East Side boutique development, this stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans over 1,200 square feet and offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and functionality. Enjoy deeded garage parking, a MASSIVE DECK and private storage for added convenience. The open-concept living area features a cozy gas fireplace, while the chef’s kitchen is outfitted with Thermador appliances, Quartz countertops, a separate dining nook and sleek modern finishes. The home offers large bedrooms including a primary suite with a spa like bath and walk-in closet. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, central A/C, and hardwood floors throughout. Thoughtfully designed for today's lifestyle, this home offers refined living in one of South Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods.
